          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/9.jpg",
            "quota": "",
            "location": "Hawaii & Napa Valley, CA",
            "title": "Sovereign Reset",
            "description": "Quiet the Noise. Find Your Center. Remember Who You Are. \n\nThe Sovereign Reset is more than a strategy session; it is a high-stakes deconstruction of the life you’ve built to make room for the life you were meant for.\n\nAt the top, the \"Echo\" of generic ambition is loudest. It tells you to do more, be more, and move faster—until your own voice is lost in the static. Located within a private sanctuary in the majestic mountains of Napa Valley, this 4-day immersive experience allows you to finally silence that external noise.\n\nThrough our Sovereign Narrative Architecture, we strip away the layers of \"who you’re supposed to be\" to reveal the unshakeable clarity required for your next decade of influence. We don’t just build a plan; we restore the person behind it. You will leave equipped to don your Mantle of Authority with unapologetic distinction.\n\nThis is where the Dreamer is restored, and the Architect is called.\n\nTHE EXPERIENCE:\n\n    Total Recalibration: A deep dive into your vision and legacy.\n\n    Specialized Mentorship: Direct, high-level strategic guidance.\n\n    Sovereign Alignment: Curated lodging in nature's serenity and bespoke cuisine designed to nourish the soul while we build the future.",
            "content_subtitle": "Quiet the Noise. Find Your Center. Remember Who You are.",
            "paragraph_1": "The Sovereign Reset is more than a strategy session; it is a high-stakes deconstruction of the life you’ve built to make room for the life you were meant for.",
            "paragraph_2": "At the top, the \"Echo\" of generic ambition is loudest. It tells you to do more, be more, and move faster—until your own voice is lost in the static. Located within a private sanctuary in the majestic mountains of Napa Valley, this 4-day immersive experience allows you to finally silence that external noise.",
            "paragraph_3": "Through our Sovereign Narrative Architecture, we strip away the layers of \"who you’re supposed to be\" to reveal the unshakeable clarity required for your next decade of influence. We don’t just build a plan; we restore the person behind it. You will leave equipped to don your Mantle of Authority with unapologetic distinction.",
            "paragraph_4": "This is where the Dreamer is restored, and the Architect is called.",
            "paragraph_5": "THE EXPERIENCE:\n\n    Total Recalibration: A deep dive into your vision and legacy.\n\n    Specialized Mentorship: Direct, high-level strategic guidance.\n\n    Sovereign Alignment: Curated lodging in nature's serenity and bespoke cuisine designed to nourish the soul while we build the future.",
