            "image": "shopify://shop_images/7.jpg",
            "quota": "",
            "location": "Hawaii & Napa Valley, CA",
            "title": "Preparing the Bride: A Sacred Immersion",
            "description": "Beyond the Veil. Before the Vow. Become the Dream.\n\nThe world prepares you for a wedding; the House of Vuu prepares you for a Legacy.\n\nIn the whirlwind of planning, guest lists, and logistics, it is easy for the Bride to lose the very woman who was first \"Fashioned for Love and Greatness.\" Preparing the Bride is a definitive, multi-dimensional immersion designed to anchor your identity before you ever walk down the aisle. This is a sanctuary for the woman who refuses to lose herself in her union, but instead chooses to enter it as her highest, most sovereign self.\n\nWithin this private mountain sanctuary, we go beyond the physical to the profound. This is where you silence the noise of the \"event\" to hear the voice of your Purpose.\nThe Internal Architecture\n\nThrough a curated blend of spiritual anchoring and emotional recalibration, we awaken the Dreamer within. We believe a sacred union is not where your individual dreams go to die, but where they are catalyzed. You will deconstruct any fear of \"losing yourself\" and replace it with an unshakeable security in who you were always meant to be. Donning the Mantle of Authority.\n\nThis is your season of elevation. You will be guided to move past the role of \"fiancée\" and step into your Mantle of Grace and Authority. You will leave refreshed, elevated, and anchored—carrying a sense of hope and passion that will fuel your marriage for decades to come.\n\nYou are not just a bride; you are a woman fashioned for a kingdom. It is time to prepare the Queen.",
            "content_subtitle": "Beyond the Veil. Before the Vow. Become the Dream.",
            "paragraph_1": "The world prepares you for a wedding; the House of Vuu prepares you for a Legacy.\n\nIn the whirlwind of planning, guest lists, and logistics, it is easy for the Bride to lose the very woman who was first \"Fashioned for Love and Greatness.\" Preparing the Bride is a definitive, multi-dimensional immersion designed to anchor your identity before you ever walk down the aisle. This is a sanctuary for the woman who refuses to lose herself in her union, but instead chooses to enter it as her highest, most sovereign self.",
            "paragraph_2": "Within this private mountain sanctuary, we go beyond the physical to the profound. This is where you silence the noise of the \"event\" to hear the voice of your Purpose.\nThe Internal Architecture",
            "paragraph_3": "Through a curated blend of spiritual anchoring and emotional recalibration, we awaken the Dreamer within. We believe a sacred union is not where your individual dreams go to die, but where they are catalyzed. You will deconstruct any fear of \"losing yourself\" and replace it with an unshakeable security in who you were always meant to be. Donning the Mantle of Authority.",
            "paragraph_4": "This is your season of elevation. You will be guided to move past the role of \"fiancée\" and step into your Mantle of Grace and Authority. You will leave refreshed, elevated, and anchored—carrying a sense of hope and passion that will fuel your marriage for decades to come.",
